headline: Interactive Brokers Group Reports Brokerage Metrics and Other Financial Information for July 2025, Includes Reg.-NMS Execution Statistics
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., August 01, 2025--Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (Nasdaq: IBKR) an automated global electronic broker, today reported its Electronic Brokerage monthly performance metrics for July.
